# Card-audit (mtg-948 Part B): Terror — destroy nonblack nonartifact creature (scripted).
#
# Closed issue mtg-549 closed Terror as WORKING but carried NO scripted puzzle
# with semantic assertions (the pre-existing terror_destroys_creature.pzl is an
# old golden-log-only puzzle with no [assertions] section, heuristic-driven).
# This audit puzzle SCRIPTS the cast and asserts the outcome.
#
# Terror is a {1}{B} instant: "Destroy target nonartifact, nonblack creature. It
# can't be regenerated." (SP$ Destroy | ValidTgts$ Creature.nonArtifact+nonBlack
# | NoRegen$ True). Destroy -> owner's graveyard (CR 701.7).
#
# Aspects exercised (issue mtg-549):
#   1. Parses + castable as a {1}{B} instant (spell cast assertion).
#   2. Targeting restriction ValidTgts$ Creature.nonArtifact+nonBlack accepts a
#      green 2/2 Grizzly Bears (nonblack, nonartifact).
#   3. Destroy effect moves the targeted creature battlefield -> owner's
#      graveyard. (Asserted by graveyard membership rather than the `creature
#      died` event, because the destroy-death event-emission widening is a
#      sibling in-flight change, mtg-961; graveyard membership is robust either
#      way.)
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0: Terror in hand, 1 Swamp + 1 Mountain to pay {1}{B}.
#   - P1: a Grizzly Bears (2/2, green) it controls.
#   - Script: P0 casts Terror at the Grizzly Bears; it is destroyed into P1's
#     graveyard.

[metadata]
Name:Card Audit - Terror Destroys a Nonblack Creature
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 scripts Terror ({1}{B} instant) at P1's green 2/2 Grizzly Bears, destroying it into P1's graveyard. Backs issue mtg-549 (Destroy over ValidTgts$ Creature.nonArtifact+nonBlack, NoRegen; CR 701.7).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=Terror
p0battlefield=Swamp;Mountain
p0library=Swamp;Swamp;Swamp;Swamp;Swamp

p1life=20
p1battlefield=Grizzly Bears
p1library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest

[p0_script]
# Destroy P1's Grizzly Bears (the only creature on the board, so the selector is
# unambiguous).
cast Terror targeting Grizzly Bears

[assertions]
# The removal instant was actually cast by the script.
spell cast Terror
# The destroyed creature is now in its owner's (P1's) graveyard. Stable
# end-state check (a destroyed creature stays in the graveyard).
opponent graveyard contains Grizzly Bears
